OL,5, Author Salman Rushdie is still in a    
OL,6, critical condition but "his usual      
OL,7, feisty and defiant sense of humour     
OL,8, remains intact", his son says.         
OL,10,FZafar Rushdie said his father had      
OL,11,Fsustained life-changing injuries, but  
OL,12,Fwas able to speak to his family.       
OL,14,FMr Rushdie, 75, was left severely      
OL,15,Finjured after being stabbed on stage at
OL,16,Fan event in New York state.            
OL,18,FHe has faced years of death threats for
OL,19,Fhis novel The Satanic Verses, which    
OL,20,Fsome Muslims see as blasphemous.       
